@host = http://localhost:3000
@correlationId = test-correlation-00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@teamsUserId   = 11111111-2222-3333-4444-555555555555

### Incoming call — backend route called by the Event Grid forwarder
POST {{host}}/calls/incoming
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rawPhone": "+493411234567",
  "correlationId": "{{correlationId}}",
  "incomingCallContext": "fake-incoming-call-context-token",
  "callerDisplayName": "Test Caller"
}

### Health check
GET {{host}}/health

### Transfer the active call to a Teams user
POST {{host}}/calls/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "correlationId": "{{correlationId}}",
  "teamsUserId": "{{teamsUserId}}"
}
